===林肯中心校园===
林肯中心校园目前有整个法学院，部分商学院、社会服务学院、和教育学院在此。<ref name="Leon Lowenstein Academic Building">{{cite web | url=http://www.fordham.edu/audience/tours/lc_map/03_Lowenstein.shtml | title=Leon Lowenstein Academic Building | accessdate=2013-06-22 | archive-date=2011-08-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110828063139/http://www.fordham.edu/audience/tours/lc_map/03_Lowenstein.shtml | dead-url=no }}</ref>本科生在这里也有一个校区，被称为福坦莫林肯中心学院（Fordham College at Lincoln Center）。<ref name="Studying at Lincoln Center">{{cite web | url=http://www.fordham.edu/academics/colleges__graduate_s/undergraduate_colleg/fordham_college_at_l/studying_at_lincoln_/index.asp | title=Studying at Lincoln Center | accessdate=2013-06-22 | archive-date=2012-09-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120917141028/http://www.fordham.edu/academics/colleges__graduate_s/undergraduate_colleg/fordham_college_at_l/studying_at_lincoln_/index.asp | dead-url=no }}</ref>学生可通过校内巴士来往玫瑰山和林肯中心，也可以坐[[纽约地铁|地铁]]或[[大都会北方通勤铁路|大都会北方通勤铁路]]。<ref name=" Discover Fordham   Maps and Directions">{{cite web | url=http://www.fordham.edu/discover_fordham/maps_and_directions_26615.asp | title=Discover Fordham   Maps and Directions | accessdate=2013-06-22 | archive-date=2014-07-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140709073808/http://www.fordham.edu/discover_fordham/maps_and_directions_26615.asp | dead-url=no }}</ref>校园中央偏西有一块不属于学校的住宅楼“阿尔弗雷德公寓”<ref name="Fordham Slams Gate to Litigious Neighbors">{{cite web | url=http://cityroom.blogs.nytimes.com/2009/12/08/fordham-slams-gate-to-litigious-neighbors/?_r=0 | title=Fordham Slams Gate to Litigious Neighbors | accessdate=2013-06-22 | archive-date=2021-02-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206050048/https://cityroom.blogs.nytimes.com/2009/12/08/fordham-slams-gate-to-litigious-neighbors/?_r=0 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，西北和西南以后也会为了筹集资金建起新的住宅楼。<ref name="Fordham University Lincoln Center Master Plan Proposal Summary" />
林肯中心校园起源于1926年法学院为了应对[[美国律师协会|美国律师协会]]增加律师资格的要求，而专门为没有本科学历的法学院录取者准备的短期大学速成班。该学院最早位于纽约下城区，后与法学院一起迁往现址。<ref name="fordham law hist">{{cite book | title=Fordham University School of Law: A History | publisher=Fordham University Press | author=Kaczorowski, Robert | year=2012 | location=New York, NY | pages=94 | isbn=9780823239559}}</ref>

因为布朗克斯校园周边治安不佳，在考虑过将校园搬到郊区的可能性<ref name="Fordham Has Big Plans for Lincoln Square Campus Comment">{{cite web| url=http://www.nysun.com/comments/36396| title=Fordham Has Big Plans for Lincoln Square Campus Comment| accessdate=2013-06-22| archive-date=2016-05-12| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160512201426/http://www.nysun.com/comments/36396| dead-url=no}}</ref>以及发现纽约市区的吸引力加强后<ref name="Fordham Has Big Plans for Lincoln Square Campus">{{cite web | url=http://www.nysun.com/real-estate/fordham-has-big-plans-for-lincoln-square-campus/59158/ | title=Fordham Has Big Plans for Lincoln Square Campus | accessdate=2013-06-22 | archive-date=2021-04-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410090833/https://www.nysun.com/real-estate/fordham-has-big-plans-for-lincoln-square-campus/59158/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>，福坦莫准备大举扩建其林肯中心校园。<ref name="Fordham University Lincoln Center Master Plan Proposal Summary">{{cite web | url=http://www.fordham.edu/fordhamuplans/proposal.html | title=Fordham University Lincoln Center Master Plan Proposal Summary | accessdate=2013-06-22 | archive-date=2008-12-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081223002201/https://www.fordham.edu/fordhamuplans/proposal.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>作为该计划的第一步，福坦莫通过出售校园西北角的一地块，获得了资金来建设新的法学院大楼和宿舍，虽然此举遭到了周边居民对于当初福坦莫获得此地条件和与纽约市政府所签合同的质疑。<ref name="Board of Estimate Approves Fordham Plan to Sell Site at Lincoln Center">{{cite web | url=http://www.nytimes.com/1989/12/25/nyregion/board-of-estimate-approves-fordham-plan-to-sell-site-at-lincoln-center.html | title=Board of Estimate Approves Fordham Plan to Sell Site at Lincoln Center | accessdate=2013-06-22 | archive-date=2020-07-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200712003129/https://www.nytimes.com/1989/12/25/nyregion/board-of-estimate-approves-fordham-plan-to-sell-site-at-lincoln-center.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>阿尔弗雷德公寓的居民甚至诉诸法律希望来阻止福坦莫扩建，但官司已被法院驳回。<ref name="Lincoln Center Expansion Lawsuit Dismissed">{{cite web | url=http://www.fordhamobserver.com/lincoln-center-expansion-lawsuit-dismissed/ | title=Lincoln Center Expansion Lawsuit Dismissed | accessdate=2013-06-22 | archive-date=2018-07-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180715094512/http://www.fordhamobserver.com/lincoln-center-expansion-lawsuit-dismissed/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>

在新法学院和宿舍在2014年投入使用后，福坦莫准备在2032年以前继续在林肯中心建设新的社会服务学院和教育学院大楼、新的商学院大楼、新的图书馆。学校西南角的一地块也有可能被出售以换取建设资金。<ref name="Fordham University Lincoln Center Master Plan Proposal Summary" />
